Package no.ntnu.idatg2001.paths.model

Class Link

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatg2001.paths.model.Link
@Entity public class Link extends Object
A class that makes it possible to move from one passage to another, by using links between the different parts of the story's plot. It contains a list of actions, a text, a reference and a story.
Version:
2023.02.02
Author:
Erik Bjørnsen and Emil Klevgård-Slåttsveen
